title: Aww! Karan Wahi’s Girlfriend Just Made Their Relationship “Insta-Official”
text:
A post shared by J E N (@jinitasheth) on Jan 5, 2017 at 12:37pm PST 
Karan Wahi is officially of the market, ladies! Karan recently was in the news for allegedly dating Jinita Sheth . He didn’t vehemently deny it at the time and their Instagram was filled with cutesy photos of themseleves. Looks like Jinita just made their relationship “insta-official” and they surely make one good-looking pair. Check it out! A post shared by J E N (@jinitasheth) on Feb 15, 2017 at 12:38am PST 21
